{"tid":613613,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個健康生活小貼士（歡迎自行補充）","createTime":"2018-04-01T19:47:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-02T01:43:48.000Z","uid":178187,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7c501113027581b34c8ad526d2fe66078aca11a6","tid":613613,"uid":178187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T19:47:33.000Z","msg":"1.飲水唔好咁大啖飲<br />\n<br />\n2.食飯之後一小時之內唔好做運動（包括散步）<br />\n<br />\n3.做完運動，流汗之後唔好即刻沖涼(起碼30分鐘後），同埋要擦背，唔好由得佢乾。<br />\n<br />\n4.做完劇烈運動後，等個心跳緩慢咗先好飲野。<br />\n<br />\n5.訓覺之前要確保頭髮係乾，唔好濕住訓。（建議早啲沖，真係唔得閒就用風筒吹）<br />\n<br />\n6.訓夠八個鐘唔代表你第二日一定會精神，最關鍵係睡眠質素。<br />\n<br />\n7.要確保睡眠質素，其中一個方法，訓覺前一個半鐘至兩個鐘沖熱水（38-40度)涼。等身體溫度係訓覺前可以下降至適當溫度。<br />\n<br />\n8.第二個方法，睡前一小時唔好接觸電子產品<br />\n<br />\n9.性愛次數不宜過多，亦不宜太少。最佳次數為一星期三次。<br />\n<br />\n10.呼吸方法：鼻吸嘴吐，忌嘴吸氣，會令下爬變形。<br />\n<br />\n11.一定要食早餐！<br />\n<br />\n12.一星期禁食一天(可以飲水)，可以更長壽，但亦增加心臟病風險。( 依個point仲係爭議緊)<br />\n<br />\n13.請勿進入中國北方範圍，為了你的肺部著想。<br />\n<br />\n14.真心朋友最緊要，有幾多豬朋狗友都唔夠一個真心朋友好，而長遠保持交流同聯絡係好重要。有好多長壽者身邊都有一班朋友。<br />\n<br />\n15.有得移民就好移民，冇得移民就算做齊上面所有野都係冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以上只係個人見解同埋傳統智慧，可能會有迷信成份，睇吓就算，唔洗咁認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a33fc967a0064793c4c5327ab80c92a8c528e10","tid":613613,"uid":5048,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T19:49:57.000Z","msg":"半夜四點唔好上連登 更加唔好開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b19aa4eb640b6dd230edde45528356200b86621","tid":613613,"uid":178187,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"7a33fc967a0064793c4c5327ab80c92a8c528e10","tid":613613,"uid":5048,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T19:49:57.000Z","msg":"半夜四點唔好上連登 更加唔好開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T19:51:26.000Z","msg":"今晚假期例外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"076ec73efb90afc33a4a93531edff37369435fba","tid":613613,"uid":178187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T19:53:51.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdc985a8ccc191e98561517d0770c146c4f7acf8","tid":613613,"uid":178187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T19:54:26.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"5267a10fe6cc3d3680ce769dae75c57360b1ab38","tid":613613,"uid":178187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T19:54:36.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"22cc7a4d9ecc73aade6274acc0b82a7980e7ca13","tid":613613,"uid":178187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T19:54:52.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"5d35ffceddc11bf579832b5c22c6b1d76911d2f8","tid":613613,"uid":178187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T19:55:27.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"2264113301472e6eaaf896d697af78e1307ba2c9","tid":613613,"uid":178187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T19:56:42.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"f4090e31084cd20c59cc1a740c6b131c2eb43085","tid":613613,"uid":178187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T19:57:52.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"bc826d5bfbc5f854b4ae3075125d2cec18d25118","tid":613613,"uid":178187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T19:58:43.000Z","msg":"78910 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d313e2e6a4b34f4717ea3f5be4920046989406b","tid":613613,"uid":52515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T20:25:49.000Z","msg":"無知一問 1係點解？"},{"pid":"f2f